actions.message:
Our Discord services simply consist of us creating new or redesigning old discord servers for any use. @Member 

You must create a ticket to find out more information on how much we will need, but here are some things we do:

- Fan Discord $8

- Roleplay Group Discords $15 (depends how much)

- Private Discords $10

- Discords which are components of another main discord $5

If you have any other discord servers you want made, we can do it for you, all you have to do is open a ticket so we can discuss how big you want it and what you want in it and other factors to determine the final amount. 
We create everything! Please open a ticket if you want one of these and we will get right on it!${member}
